<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="keywords" content="" />
<meta name="description" content="" />
<meta name="author" content="zhoujiqiu"/>
<title>惠普仓储管理系统-登录</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/main.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hh_logo">
        <h1><a href="#"><img src="/images/hh_logo.png"></a></h1></div>
    <div class="logo_box">
        <div class="logo_form">
            <h3>请输入Email和密码进入管理系统</h3>
            {% set form = activeform.begin({'id':'create-form','layout':'horizontal','fieldConfig':{'horizontalCssClasses':{'wrapper':'item'} } }) %}
                {{ form.field(model,'email',{inputOptions:{'class':'form-control'}}).label(null,{'class':'control-label col-lg-3'})|raw}}
                {{ form.field(model,'password',{inputOptions:{'class':'form-control'}}).passwordInput().label(null,{'class':'control-label col-lg-3'})|raw}}
                <div class="clear"></div>
                <div class="remember">
                    <label><input type="checkbox" name="remember" value="0"> 记住密码</label>
                </div>
                <div class="post">
                    <input type="submit" name="" value="&nbsp;" class="login_btn">
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="notice_box">
            <ul>
                {% for data in news %}
                <li>{{ data.content }} {{ data.created|date('Y-m-d')}}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>本系统为HH China为惠普中国特别定制。&copy;2015 北京宏昊寰宇国际贸易有限公司版权所有。</p>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery-1.7.2.min.js"></script>
    <script type='text/javascript' src='/js/base.js'></script>
</body>
</html>